It's so hot in here.
You hot?

32:42.695 --> 32:44.494
Yeah.

32:44.496 --> 32:46.163
Burning up.

32:48.033 --> 32:49.199
Buttons are hard.
[ chuckles ]

32:49.201 --> 32:50.400
Let me give you a hand.

32:50.402 --> 32:52.169
[ chuckles ]

32:52.171 --> 32:53.470
Thank you.

32:53.472 --> 32:56.073
[ chuckles ]

32:56.075 --> 32:58.642
You know, I can't believe
there was ever a day

32:58.644 --> 33:01.011
