you were nobody special.

33:02.715 --> 33:04.181
You're extraordinary,
scarlett.

33:05.751 --> 33:07.351
First minute
I met you --

33:07.353 --> 33:10.120
I-I mean,
<i> second</i> time I met you

33:10.122 --> 33:12.022
Thinking it was
the first time...

33:13.359 --> 33:15.125
...I knew
you'd change my life.

33:19.331 --> 33:21.631
Let's, uh...

33:21.633 --> 33:23.767
Play one of our old ones.

